OL,7,FJersey's Privileges and Procedures
OL,8,FCommittee has lodged a proposition
OL,9,Frecommending the suspension of Deputy
OL,10,FPhilip Ozouf for 28 days without pay.
OL,12,FThe Committee's recommendations were
OL,13,Fmade following an investigation that
OL,14,Ffound Deputy Ozouf breached the
OL,15,FStates' Code of Conduct on multiple
OL,16,Foccasions.
