OL,3,CJersey politician threatened with
OL,4,Cunpaid suspension for Code of Conduct
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FIt follows an incident in late
OL,8,FNovember last year where the deputy
OL,9,Fwas caught driving at 31mph in a 15mph
OL,10,Fzone without displaying valid car
OL,11,Finsurance.
OL,13,FThe case was ultimately escalated to
OL,14,Fthe Magistrate's court, where he was
OL,15,Ffined #575.
OL,17,FDeputy Ozouf made a voluntary apology
OL,18,Ffor his behaviour in connection with
OL,19,Fthis incident in the States Assembly
OL,20,Fon 19 March 2025.
