OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FBut the island's Commissioner for
OL,8,FStandards has now found Deputy Ozouf
OL,9,Fhas breached Paragraphs 2, 3, 4, and 5
OL,10,Fof the Code of Conduct.
OL,12,FThese violations relate to his ability
OL,13,Fto uphold the law, adhere to the Seven
OL,14,FPrinciples of Public Life, act in the
OL,15,Fpublic interest above any private
OL,16,Finterests, and uphold public trust.
