OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FThe report detailing the breaches
OL,8,Fstates that "elected representatives
OL,9,Fare expected to model lawful behaviour
OL,10,Fand demonstrate respect for due
OL,11,Fprocess".
OL,13,FIt found that Deputy Ozouf's actions
OL,14,F"did not meet the standards of
OL,15,Fleadership, integrity, and
OL,16,Faccountability expected of those
OL,17,Fholding public office".
