OL,3,CJersey politician threatened with
OL,4,Cunpaid suspension for Code of Conduct
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FThe report also detailed that Deputy
OL,8,FOzouf failed to engage with the
OL,9,Finvestigation process in a timely and
OL,10,Fconstructive manner, after he failed
OL,11,Fto attend three separate summons by
OL,12,Fthe Parish Hall in St Helier.
OL,14,FThe Privileges and Procedures
OL,15,FCommittee have thus recommended the
OL,16,Fpolitician be suspended without pay
OL,17,Ffor the maximum period of 28 days.
