OL,3,CJersey politician threatened with
OL,4,Cunpaid suspension for Code of Conduct
OL,5,Cbreaches
OL,7,FThey state this sanction would be
OL,8,Fproportionate, given Deputy Ozouf
OL,9,Fbreached the Code on numerous counts
OL,10,Fand has demonstrated "a lack of regard
OL,11,Ffor the Island's Laws and judicial
OL,12,Fprocess".
OL,14,FThey add that his actions have
OL,15,F"damaged the integrity and reputation
OL,16,Fof the Assembly".
OL,18,FThe proposition will be voted on by
OL,19,Fthe Assembly at the next States
OL,20,Fmeeting on 9 September.
